		<h1><a href="https://sleddogwatchdog.wordpress.com/2017/06/21/churchill-manitoba-canada-sled-dogs-as-polar-bear-bait/" rel="bookmark">Churchill, Manitoba, Canada: Sled Dogs as Polar Bear Bait</a></h1>
				<div class="timestamp"><a href="https://sleddogwatchdog.wordpress.com/2017/06/21/churchill-manitoba-canada-sled-dogs-as-polar-bear-bait/" rel="bookmark" title="Permalink to Churchill, Manitoba, Canada: Sled Dogs as Polar Bear Bait">June 21, 2017</a> //</div> <div class="comment-bubble"><a href="https://sleddogwatchdog.wordpress.com/2017/06/21/churchill-manitoba-canada-sled-dogs-as-polar-bear-bait/#respond">0</a></a></div>		<div class="clearboth"><!-- --></div>

		
	</div>

	<div class="post-content">
		<p>&#8220;This is one of the worst cases of CLASSIC passive cruelty currently existing in Canada.&#8221; (Courtesy of CFAWR.org)<a href="https://sleddogwatchdog.files.wordpress.com/2017/06/3842ecb0-ff5d-49b9-84ce-ded547381b58.jpg"><img data-attachment-id="558" data-permalink="https://sleddogwatchdog.wordpress.com/3842ecb0-ff5d-49b9-84ce-ded547381b58/" data-orig-file="https://sleddogwatchdog.files.wordpress.com/2017/06/3842ecb0-ff5d-49b9-84ce-ded547381b58.jpg" data-orig-size="594,662" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="3842ecb0-ff5d-49b9-84ce-ded547381b58" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://sleddogwatchdog.files.wordpress.com/2017/06/3842ecb0-ff5d-49b9-84ce-ded547381b58.jpg?w=269" data-large-file="https://sleddogwatchdog.files.wordpress.com/2017/06/3842ecb0-ff5d-49b9-84ce-ded547381b58.jpg?w=460" src="https://sleddogwatchdog.files.wordpress.com/2017/06/3842ecb0-ff5d-49b9-84ce-ded547381b58.jpg?w=460" alt=""   class="alignnone size-full wp-image-558" srcset="https://sleddogwatchdog.files.wordpress.com/2017/06/3842ecb0-ff5d-49b9-84ce-ded547381b58.jpg?w=460 460w, https://sleddogwatchdog.files.wordpress.com/2017/06/3842ecb0-ff5d-49b9-84ce-ded547381b58.jpg?w=135 135w, https://sleddogwatchdog.files.wordpress.com/2017/06/3842ecb0-ff5d-49b9-84ce-ded547381b58.jpg?w=269 269w, https://sleddogwatchdog.files.wordpress.com/2017/06/3842ecb0-ff5d-49b9-84ce-ded547381b58.jpg 594w" sizes="(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px"/></a></p>

